      "writtenOn": "2019-08-25T01:47:32Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "It seemed that every OutputStreamInterface implementation probably should have flush_needed_ logic, do you refer to have base class in this case? Maybe, the implementations will have its own handling of flush_need_, it makes flush_needed_ not connivence in a base class.",
