      "message": "There isn’t much value to building a vector for this at runtime. I would do:\n\n  static constexpr size_t kWriteLengths[] \u003d {4, 96, 40, …};\n\nand loop over it as:\n\n  for (size_t index \u003d 0; index \u003c base::size(kWriteLengths); ++index)",
